cdata.name: Quantler
cdata.desc:
Quantler is a software company based in the Netherlands. Itprovides the users with a set of tools to assistthem to create and develop cryptocurrency investment products. Note thatis the user who controls its own funds, Quantler does not offerinvestment management services.

The QUANT tokenis an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is the token that supports and fuels the platform as it is needed for the user to host a Quant Fund at Quantler.
